N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 326.11 - Storage

State Regulations

No person shall store any restricted pesticide or empty
containers thereof in such a manner as may be injurious to human, plant or
animal life or to property or which unreasonably interferes with the
comfortable enjoyment of life and property throughout such areas of the State
as shall be affected thereby. Notes
